name: Packing Home (Cloud1337, AimoutoWolf)
description: A small game made for the Quarantine Jam where I was the programmer and AimoutoWolf is the Artist. All assets in the game are originally made with the exception of some textures and there is no music atm since we didn't find anything to our tastes and lack of licenses. Hope you enjoy and any feedback will be ignored (not really but really).
